Gargiulo is also being held for the December 2005 stabbing of Maria Bruno in her El Monte, Los Angeles apartment.

According to police in Chicago, Gargiulo was a family friend of 18- year-old Miss Pacaccio, who was found by her father in August 1993 on the step of her Chicago home after she had been stabbed 12 times.

